ax-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">23.移动端字体单位font-size选择px还是rem？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">// 如需适配多种移动设备，建议使用rem。以下为参考值：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">html { font-size: 62.5%; } //10*16 = 62.5%</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">//设置12px字体 这里注意在rem前要加上对应的px值，解决不支持rem的浏览器的兼容问题，做到优雅降级</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">body { font-size:12px; font-size:1.2rem; }</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">24.input标签添加上disable属性在ios端字体颜色不兼容的问题？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><pre class=\"brush:css;toolbar:false\">input[disabled],input:disabled,input.disabled{\r\n\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;color:&nbsp;#3e3e3e;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;-webkit-text-fill-color:&nbsp;#3e3e3e;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;-webkit-opacity:1;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;opacity:&nbsp;1;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n}</pre><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">25.IOS 的光标大小问题</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">IE：不管该行有没有文字，光标高度与font-size一致。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">FF：该行有文字时，光标高度与font-size一致。该行无文字时，光标高度与input的height一致。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">Chrome：该行无文字时，光标高度与line-height一致；该行有文字时，光标高度从input顶部到文字底部(这两种情况都是在有设定line-height的时候)，如果没有line-height，则是与font-size一致。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">IOS中情况和Chrome 相似。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">设置字体大小和行高一致，然后通过 padding 撑开大小</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">只给IE浏览器设置 line-height</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">-ms-line-height:40px;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p>');
INSERT INTO `myblog_article` VALUES ('13', '1536488592.jpg', '【Ajax】实现实时搜索框提示功能', '1536488592', '作品', '分享搜索框提示功能的实例代码', '<p>分享一下实现的原理,示例图后贴上代码<br/></p><p><br/></p><p>示例图:</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">搜索带有学院关键字的文章标题</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180909/1536488851688058.jpg\" title=\"1536488851688058.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">搜索带有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">西京</span>关键字的文章标题</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180909/1536488975288598.jpg\" title=\"1536488975288598.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">搜索带有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">新生</span>关键字的文章标题<br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180909/1536488957375326.jpg\" title=\"1536488957375326.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>前端代码<br/></p><p><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:html;toolbar:false\">&lt;!doctype&nbsp;html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;meta&nbsp;charset=&quot;utf-8&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;title&gt;搜索界面&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&lt;meta&nbsp;http-equiv=&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot;&nbsp;content=&quot;IE=edge&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;meta&nbsp;name=&quot;viewport&quot;&nbsp;content=&quot;width=device-width,&nbsp;initial-scale=1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;link&nbsp;rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&nbsp;href=&quot;../bs/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;script&nbsp;src=&quot;../bs/js/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;script&nbsp;src=&quot;../bs/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\n	\r\n	.list-group-item{\r\n		border:none;\r\n	}\r\n	.main{\r\n		background:&nbsp;#FDFDFD;\r\n		border:&nbsp;1px&nbsp;solid&nbsp;#333;\r\n		display:&nbsp;none;\r\n	}\r\n	&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n&lt;div&nbsp;class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;input&nbsp;type=&quot;text&quot;&nbsp;class=&quot;form-control&quot;&nbsp;id=&quot;text&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&nbsp;class=&quot;main&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div&nbsp;class=&quot;list-group&quot;&gt;\r\n	\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;script&gt;\r\n	\r\n$(function(){\r\n		\r\n	$(&quot;#text&quot;).keyup(function(){\r\n			\r\n		val=$(this).val();\r\n					\r\n		if(val.length!=0){\r\n		\r\n		$.ajax({\r\n				\r\n		type:&quot;post&quot;,\r\n				\r\n		url:&quot;search.php&quot;,\r\n				\r\n		data:{&quot;data&quot;:val},\r\n				\r\n		success:function(data){\r\n				\r\n			if(data==0){\r\n						\r\n			}else{\r\n						\r\n				$(&quot;.main&quot;).css(&quot;display&quot;,&quot;block&quot;);\r\n						\r\n				$(&quot;.list-group&quot;).html(data);\r\n			}\r\n	\r\n		}\r\n	});\r\n			\r\n}else{\r\n			\r\n	$(&quot;.main&quot;).css(&quot;display&quot;,&quot;none&quot;);\r\n			\r\n}\r\n\r\n});\r\n});\r\n	\r\n	\r\n&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p><br/></p><p>PHP代码</p><p><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\">&lt;?php\r\n\r\nerror_reporting(0);\r\n\r\n/*	$arr为模拟从数据库中取出的文章标题		(二维数组)	*/\r\n\r\n$arr=[\r\n	\r\n	[&quot;uid&quot;=&gt;1,&quot;title&quot;=&gt;&quot;西京学院秉承一切为了学生的发展理念&quot;],\r\n	[&quot;uid&quot;=&gt;2,&quot;title&quot;=&gt;&quot;创业书院&quot;],\r\n	[&quot;uid&quot;=&gt;3,&quot;title&quot;=&gt;&quot;渭南师范学院&quot;],\r\n	[&quot;uid&quot;=&gt;4,&quot;title&quot;=&gt;&quot;新生饭卡查找&quot;],\r\n	[&quot;uid&quot;=&gt;5,&quot;title&quot;=&gt;&quot;新生军训守则&quot;]\r\n	\r\n];	\r\n\r\n\r\n$data=$_POST[&#39;data&#39;];\r\n\r\n\r\nforeach($arr&nbsp;as&nbsp;$key=&gt;$val){\r\n	\r\n	$uidArr[]=$val[&#39;uid&#39;];	//	数据表中uid中的集合\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	$ex=explode($data,$val[&#39;title&#39;]);\r\n	\r\n	if(count($ex)&gt;1){\r\n		$arr2[]=$key;	//记录拥有关键字标题的索引\r\n	}\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\nif(empty($arr2)){	//如果没有查找到关键字\r\n	return&nbsp;0;\r\n	\r\n}else{\r\n	\r\n	$json=array();\r\n	\r\n	for($i=0;$i&lt;count($arr2);$i++){\r\n		\r\n		$num=$arr2[$i];\r\n		\r\n		$json[]=$arr[$num][&#39;title&#39;];\r\n		\r\n	}\r\n	\r\nforeach($json&nbsp;as&nbsp;$val){\r\n	echo&nbsp;&quot;&lt;a&nbsp;class=&#39;list-group-item&#39;&gt;$val&lt;/a&gt;&quot;;\r\n}\r\n	\r\n\r\n}\r\n?&gt;</pre>');

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for `myblog_comment`
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `myblog_comment`;
CREATE TABLE `myblog_comment` (
  `uid` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `info` text NOT NULL,
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `time` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`uid`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=13 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

